{"tid":505362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【自行了斷】樂視香港入稟申請自行清盤","createTime":"2017-12-21T04:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T12:09:42.000Z","uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"110dfc0ce46ef53553fb08bac878409d273842e2","tid":505362,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:40:05.000Z","msg":"官非纏身的樂視香港，最於入稟法院自行清盤！根據法庭文件顯示，樂視有限公司（LE Corporation Limited）入稟法院，以自行清盤方式申請清盤。並已排期於明年2月21日提訊。<br />\n<br />\n樂視於2015年攻港，成立樂視體育，其後投行香港英超及NBA賽事獨家播映權，於今年11月樂視體育出售世界盃播映權予電盈（008）旗下的now及viutv。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8529576fc645f0adb77e1279579c44d548fb71","tid":505362,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1730138/%E6%A8%82%E8%A6%96%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E6%B8%85%E7%9B%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F1730138%2F%25E6%25A8%2582%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%25A8%259F%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25A1%258C%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%259B%25A4&d=pLN3bEDIYDO9G7KjYHSZGzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=5044c6aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/1730138/%E6%A8%82%E8%A6%96%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%A5%E7%A8%9F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%87%AA%E8%A1%8C%E6%B8%85%E7%9B%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n信報既鏈結.."},{"pid":"507719e02a698f9514842d0ab01a7011fd871888","tid":505362,"uid":160586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T11:39:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97c85d1cd8d4f3e107984d62a5fe39a2c0fcf3db","tid":505362,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20